improve:
- I would have liked to see some short sentences about data usage/privacy explaining where the data are stored and for which purposes can be used and by who
- I am not 100% sure that the outcome collection is set up in a way that is temporarily consistent with the treatment schedule. For example, I wanted to do an experiment in which the exposure is dinner time and the outcome is a sleep quality index. Of course the outcome needs to be recorded after the sleep, therefore the subsequent morning. I am not 100% sure I managed to set this up since the app asks me to enter my sleep index (because I used 10 am as time for outcome collection) but clearly the exposure did not happen yet.
